title: Iced Blue By Keep It 100 (OG Blue Iced)
description: OG Blue Iced formerly known as Blue Slushie Iced is a truly refreshing mixed berry vape with an icy menthol blast. Keep It 100 matches the tasty mixed berry blend e juice that will remind you of your favorite blue frozen drink from the convenience store. Just like the real thing and every bit as refreshing. This delicious mixed berry and menthol ejuice makes for a truly satisfying vaping experience that will definitely become your new all day vape.
